I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1565 as follows:
1. On Page 2, Line 15, by inserting after the letter “C.” and before the number “1.”, the
following language: “Contingent upon federal approval and disbursement of additional federal
funds for nutrition support services within the TMaH Model:”;
2. On Page 2, Line 20, by deleting after the word “outcomes”, the period “.” and inserting a
semicolon “;”;
3. On Page 3, Line 4, by deleting after the word “intake”, the period “.” and inserting the
following language: “; and”; and
4. By amending the title to conform.
